title: Speed Ex
description: Speed Ex is a dynamic race for your computer, in an incredible world full of obstacles and ludicrous speeds. Race at a high speeds through a tunnel, avoiding obstacles and collecting shields. The game will please you with its graphics and captivate fans of dynamic music, because in this game features incredible music that will have you using headphones. Turn on the turbo mode in this game and check your reaction and endurance, going as far as possible by breaking all the records and setting your own. Start the game now!
